6 SECTION 19. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1151.26, is
7 amended to read as follows:
8 Section 1151.26. A. There is hereby established the Committee
9 of Roofing Examiners, which shall consist of seven (7) members. All
10 members shall be legal residents of the United States and shall be
11 residents of this state. Members shall hold office for terms of two
12 (2) years or until their successors have been appointed and
13 qualified.
14 B. Members of the Committee shall be appointed as follows:
15 1. One member shall be appointed by the Governor and shall be a
16 licensed architect with a minimum of five (5) years' experience in
17 commercial roof design. This member shall be selected from a list
18 of at least three qualified and eligible architects submitted by a
19 state organization representing architects;
20 2. One member shall be appointed by the Governor and shall be a
21 licensed engineer with a minimum of five (5) years' experience in
22 commercial roof design. This member shall be selected from a list of
23 at least three qualified and eligible engineers submitted by a state
24 organization representing engineers;
