5 3. Assist and advise the Board on the examinations for
6 applicants for a commercial or residential roofer endorsement of the
7 Roofing Contractor Registration Act and rules thereof, and on all
8 matters relating to the commercial and residential roofer
9 endorsement provisions of the Roofing Contractor Registration Act;
